FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENT DOCUMENT (FRD)

1Ô∏è‚É£ System Overview
A Python-based web application using:
Flask (Web UI)
Selenium (Automation)
OpenAI API (AI text generation)
Excel (Tracking)

2Ô∏è‚É£ Functional Modules

üîπ Module 1: Resume Parser
FR-01
System shall upload and read .docx resume.
FR-02
System shall extract complete textual content.
FR-03
System shall validate file type.

üîπ Module 2: Job Description Analyzer
FR-04
System shall accept JD via text input.
FR-05
System shall extract keywords using NLP/Regex.
FR-06
System shall remove stopwords.

üîπ Module 3: Keyword Matching Engine
FR-07
System shall calculate keyword match percentage.
Formula:
Match % = (Matched Keywords / Total JD Keywords) * 100

FR-08
System shall display match score on UI.

üîπ Module 4: Resume Customizer (AI)
FR-09
System shall send resume summary + JD to AI API.
FR-10
System shall rewrite summary professionally.
FR-11
System shall handle API failure with retry (3 attempts).

üîπ Module 5: Cover Letter Generator
FR-12
System shall generate cover letter based on:
Role
Company
Skills
FR-13
System shall allow download in .docx format.

üîπ Module 6: Auto Apply Engine
FR-14
System shall login to selected portal.
FR-15
System shall search jobs based on keywords.
FR-16
System shall detect "Easy Apply".
FR-17
System shall auto-fill application form.
FR-18
System shall skip jobs with captcha.

üîπ Module 7: Application Tracker
FR-19
System shall create Excel file if not exists.
FR-20
System shall append job details.
Columns:
| Company | Role | Platform | Status | Date |

üîπ Module 8: Error Handling
FR-21
System shall log errors in log file.
FR-22
System shall retry API failures.
FR-23
System shall handle file read errors.

